\id PHM - Bekwel Bible 
\toc3 Flm 
\toc2 Filemɔŋ 
\toc1 Mɛkana ɛ Pɔl, pɛ daa Filemɔŋ 
\mt1 Mɛkana ɛ Pɔl, yii pɛ dáa Filemɔŋ 
\mt2 Filemɔŋ 
\c 1  
\ms1 Mɛkɛn 
\p Filemɔ nabɛɛ mɔɔ sɔ ɛ Pɔl mot lwoma. Pɔl ɛ nagoola nyɛ Mbɛɛ Bhaadal, tin, nyɛ ɛ́ boodi myalel keletyɛ. Filemɔ nabɛɛ mot ekum, nyɛ nabaadiɛ nɛ ekwom bot. Onezin nabɛɛ ngɔt tɔ ekwom ɛ Filemɔ. Tin, nyɛ naakaab kukuma yɛ, wɔ gwaa nyɛ kɛboma nɛ Pɔl pɛ nyɛ nadi tɔ mbok ɛ. É di'enek, Onezin tak nabɛɛ nyɛ moo yɛ myalel keletyɛ. Deenek, Pɔl naazɛswal Onezin pɛ daa kukuma yɛ Filemɔ nɛ ɛtom ɛ mɛkana. Filemɔ aakoomyaal Onezin pɛ yɛ tin dáa? Mɛkana mɛ Pɔl nakyeed pɛ daa Filemɔ ɛ nabaadiɛ yii bot ɛ zɛɛga mendjaala ee bɛ nadi esɛɛga tɔ ndjaŋ'ɛ (ɛlaŋel ebá). Mɛkana mɛ tak lii ɛ tɛp di gwyák bot ɛ zɛɛga mendjaala djas. Eghɛŋ yenek, ekum e kyee dik djas eLɔm nadi edjɛɛd ɛ nadyeebadus ɛ tɔ mɛsa mɛ ekwom bot. Tin, mɛtaŋ mɛ ekwom e bot nazobaadi ɛ djala nɛ mɛtaŋ mɛ bɛ nakuma dɛl. Ekwom tak nadi esesa ɛ membi mɛ mɛsa djas, bɛ nabaadiɛ «ghughumaa» si mɛko mɛ ekukuma bɔɔ. Ɛkaab ɛ kwom ngɔt goka ɛ, nyɛ tiigaa ɛlyelɛpe, ye ɛ́ nɛ ghwyil kum nyɛ ɛsyee. Tɔ mɛkana mɛ nyɛ nakwyal ɛ, Pɔl nawaab nɛ Filemɔ ɛ náá nyɛ myaal Onezin nɛ mbɛɛ lyem dáa mɔn nyɛɛg keletyɛ. Etɛɛ náá, kwom mot nɛ nakuma dɛl, bɔɔ djas ɛ bɔn nyɛɛg tɔ ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Yezu Klisto. Tin, Pɔl nabɛɛ ààdjɛ ɛlee nɛ Filemɔ, nyɛ nakwyɛl ɛ náá Filemɔ sa dáa nyɛ di kwos ɛ. Ekeletyɛ mɛkɛn, e yɔbɔ ghɛŋ, bɛ nabɛɛ ààbɛ nɛ ghwyil ɛswola embee esesɛɛ zeetawa tɔ bhwak ɛ. Tin, ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Yezu Klisto ɛ di swola mbee tsik tɔ etɛp e bhwak. Mɛlyo mɛ kwyɛl ɛ nɛ ghwyil ɛ swola tsik mot tɔ sɔ, baaswola dɔɔ nɛ tsik mɛdhuu mɛ bot. 
\s1 Mɛswosel 
\p  
\v 1 Ye ɛ́ mam Pɔl, mot membok kɔ esu ɛ mesa mɛ mɛ di esa étɛp ɛ Yezu Klisto ɛ. Bis nɛ Timote mɔɔ nyaag'am ɛ kwyal mɛkana mak. Bis kwyal mɛkana mak ɛ étɛp'ɔ wɔy Filemɔ, mɔn nyɛɛg'es bis dibaakwyɛl ɛbuɛpe tɔ mɛsa mɛ Zɛɛb ɔ.  
\v 2 Bis kwyal ɛ bot ɛ zɛɛga mendjaala mɛ di esael tɔ ndjaŋ'ɔ yenek, zɛnɔɔ kɛl'ena Apiya bɛ nɛ mɔn nyɛɛg'ena Alsipe mot bis nɛ bɛ nɔɔ di eduu tuub wat ɔ:  
\v 3 Beta náá: bi bela mbɛɛ bhwoob nɛ egwyem e mis mɛ Zɛɛb sɛɛg'ena nɛ Yawe, Yezu Klisto. 
\s1 Kwyɛl nɛ ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Zɛɛb ɛ Filemɔ 
\p  
\v 4 E sok djas mɛ di edjaala Zɛɛb ɛ, wɔy Filemɔ, mɛ nɛ djaala étɛp'ɔ, bhii tak mɛ ɛpeghapɛɛ Zɛɛb kɔ ɛsu ɛ lɔ,  
\v 5 etɛɛ náá, mɛ ɛpegwak menduk mɛ ɛdum ɛ koŋ ɛ lɔ nɛ kwyɛl Yezu Klisto nɛ dáa wɔ di nɛ lyem kwyɛl nɛ bot ɛ zeliig elyem étɛp ɛdu Ghɛŋ.  
\v 6 Mɛ waab nɛ Zɛɛb ɛ náá, ɛdum ɛ koŋ nɛ Zɛɛb di ewa ɛgwakel pak'ena ɛ nyen tɔ tsik'ena. Sa náá, enɛm ee sa djas bis di esa kɔ ɛsu ɛ Klisto ɛ baanyen.  
\v 7 Mɔn nyɛɛg, mɛkwyɛla eedjɛ mɛ mɛmyaala nɛ mɛghaaz ɛbuɛpe etɛɛ náá, wóó diaa djɛ ghwyil nɛ kwyee bot ɛ di myaal mɛkpa ɛ Zɛɛb ɔɔ ɛlyelɛpe. 
\s1 Gwyes Pɔl naadi nɛ yɛ é dum ɛ Oneezim ɛ 
\p  
\v 8 Ye nakoozodi náá, mɛ ɛ́ nɛ ghwyil dum nɛ Klisto náá, mɛ lwom wɔ, wɔ sa sa wɔ di egoka nɛ ɛsa ɛ.  
\v 9 Tin, kɔ ɛsu ɛ mɛkwyɛla mɛ mena di nɛ ye ɛ, mɛ kwyɛl ɛ ɛwaab ze nɛ nɔ. Mam Pɔl, tɔa-mot, baazɛbela náá, mɛ ɛ́ kɔɔla é membok kɔ esu ɛ din ɛ Yezu Klisto,  
\v 10 mɛ eemɛt wɔ ɛboŋ kɔ ɛsu ɛ Onezim mot di mɔn'am kɔ ɛsu ɛ ɛdum ɛ koŋ tɔ ndjaa membok wak ɔ.  
\v 11 É ghɛŋ sok, nyɛ nabɛ ɛ ààbɛ vaŋ mot é mis mɔ. Deenek, é dwoo pan mos'ak nyɛ moo ɛ́ nɛ boo mɛtaŋ dum nɛ ɛkwyee ɛ nyɛ di ekwyee wɔy nɛ mam tɔ mɛsa ɛ. 
\p  
\v 12 Nenak yak, mɛ ɛpeswaal wɔ nwyak, wɔ goka ɛ́, wɔ bee nyɛ dáa dhiiti kyee nyel'am wat.  
\v 13 Mɛ nakwyɛl ɛ náá, nyɛ lik wak é ngwoob'am étɛp nyɛ neekwyekwyee mɛ é di yɔ pɛ pak mɛ di tɔ membok kɔ ɛsu ɛ mbɛɛ bhaadal'ak.  
\v 14 Tin, mɛ nabɛ ààkwyɛl ɛsa dhiiti sonok ààpookodji wɔ. Mɛ nadi é kaab ɛ, ye ɛ́ zɛkɛdi tyee náá, enɛm ee esa wɔ aasa nɛ nam ɛ di tyee bhel. Etɛɛ náá, mot goka ɛ́ nɛ ɛsa enɛm ee esa nɛ lyem ɛmet. 
\p  
\v 15 Ye ɛ́ nɛ ghwyil ɛdi náá, Oneezim nadus wɔ e mɛmbɔ ɛ étɛp ba ɛwala batsa etɛɛ náá, nyɛ ka bula ɔ, nyɛ ka bula ɛ, bula wat na kɔm-kɔm.  
\v 16 Etɛɛ náá, kana dwoo pan mos'ak, nàka baabee nyɛ dáa kwomɔ. Bea nyɛ nɛ mɛtaŋ dhaa kwom: Etɛɛ náá, nyɛ moo ɛ́ mɔn nyɛɛg'ena mot mena di kwyɛl ɛbuɛpe ɔ. Nyɛ ɛ́ nɛ boo mɛtaŋ e mis mam nɛ e mis mɔ. Tin, ye goka ɛ́ náá nyɛ di nɛ boo mɛtaŋ e mis mɔ dhaa dhaŋa yam, tɔ mɛfulu mɛ, nɛ dáa nyɛ di kɛbɛ nɛ Ghɛŋ ɛ. 
\p  
\v 17 Ye ɛ́ bɛ náá, wɔ ɛ́ pe duwal mɛ dáa mɔɔ sɔɔ, nɔŋa nyɛ dáa wɔ di zyɛ nɛ bee mɛ ɛ.  
\v 18 Ye ɛ́ bɛ náá, nyɛ naasa wɔ ɛbiyo ɔ, nɛghu ye kabɛ náá, nyɛ naakola wɔ dhiiti sonok ɔ, kɛla tɛp tak kɔ lo'am. Mɛ waatuud wɔ yɛ mam ɛmet.  
\v 19 Mɛ kwyal mɛkana mak ɛ nɛ mbɔ'am met. É tɛp tak ɛ mɛ di elɛɛ náá: mam Pɔl, mɛ waatuud wɔ esa ee nyɛ nakola pɛ daa lɔ ɛ. Wɔ ààdjak náá, boo keede wɔ di nɛ yɛ nam mos ɛ ye ɛ́ tsik wɔ di nɛ yɛ yenek.  
\v 20 Yɛ deenek mɔn nyɛɛg, mɛ eekwyit wɔ mɛboŋ si, saaa sa, mɛ waab nɛ nɔɔ, kɔ ɛsu ɛ́ mɛkwyɛla mɛ mena di nɛ yɛ nɛ din ɛ Ghɛŋ ɛ. Mɛ kwyɛl ɛ́ wɔ sa náá lyem'am di tɔ ghwyil nɛ mɛghaaz nɛ din ɛ Klisto. 
\p  
\v 21 Lyem'am nɛ ɛmyaal nɛ ɛgwak ɛ lɔ, etɛɛ náá, é di mɛ di ekwyal mɛkana mak, é ghɛŋ wɔ waalaa mɛkana mak ɔ, waazosa ɛ dáa mɛ ke ɛ. Mɛ nɛ gu náá, wɔ aasa dhaa-dhaŋak yee mɛ ke náá wɔ sa ɛ.  
\v 22 É di'enek wat, koobela mɛ dhɛŋ etɛɛ náá, ɛbwaalel ɛ lam náá, kɔ ɛsu ɛ́ mendjaala mɛ bi di djaala étɛp'am ɛ, mɛ waabulelaa e mbɔ men. 
\s1 Mɛswosel mɛ mɛsik 
\p  
\v 23 Epafalas, mot bis nɛ nɛ di e membok étɛp din ɛ Yezu Klisto ɔ ee baaswos wɔ,  
\v 24 zɛnɔɔ Malak, Aalistaalak, Dhemas nɛ Luk, bot ɛ bis nɛ bɛ nɔɔ di sa mɛsa e di wat ɔ. 
\p  
\v 25 Betka náá, Zɛɛb tel bin enɛm nɛ embɛɛ ee Ghɛŋ'ena Yezu Klisto di kɔ len.